@greeting
Elder: Welcome, brave adventurers.
Elder: Monsters have been emerging from the Crystal Cave.
Elder: The darkness grows stronger each day...
Elder: Please, you must restore the Crystal's light.

@quest
Elder: The Wind Crystal lies deep within the cave.
Elder: Beware the undead that guard its chambers.
Elder: May the light of the Crystals guide you.

@thanks
Elder: You have restored the Crystal's light!
Elder: The kingdom is forever in your debt.
Elder: Take this as a token of our gratitude.
